News Portal Application
Revision: 0.0.8
Date: 6-23-2007

TO-DO List...

    1] Comments system / Discussion.
    2] PostGres / SQLite support.
       
######################################

--------------------------------------

Revision 0.0.1:

    Initial Concept...
    
--------------------------------------

Revision 0.0.2:

    nemesis.pl:
        * Integration of Suicide.pm ( system classes ) with tvs...
        
--------------------------------------

Revision 0.0.3:

    nemesis.pl:
        * Switched to DBI from DBM::Deep...
        
--------------------------------------

Revision 0.0.4:

    nemesis.pl:
        * Integration of spidey.pl ( news aggrigator script by ispy ) with tvs...
        
--------------------------------------

Revision 0.0.5:

    nemesis.pl:
        * Added 'article pruning' and various code refinements...
        
--------------------------------------

Revision 0.0.6:

    nemesis.pl:
        * Created 'clean_xhtml' method for stripping / encoding html strings...
        * Finished RSS/XML subscription method ( site_feed.rss generation ) ...
        
--------------------------------------

Revision 0.0.7:

    nemesis.pl:
        * Newly inserted 'feeds.xml' entry detection.  Before, any time you added a new
          news feed you had to re-build the entire dbase from scratch.  An OBVIOUS addition...
        * Cleaned up SQL syntax, but learned current syntax won't work with anything
          other than MySQL server 4 and 5. ( AUTO_INCREMENT not good I suppose )
        
--------------------------------------

Revision 0.0.8:

    nemesis.pl:
        * Re-named all TVSuicide::Engine methods to comply with 'set, get, do' pragma... ( better OO naming scheme )
        * Re-defined and developed a more extensible and less memory intensive Object-Oriented class structure.
        * NO MORE GLOBAL VARIABLES! TVS now uses local lexical variables and references only now.  This was
          the true goal of this revision.
        
